      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLINDSPOT (1) has a strong record this track and trip with three wins and three placings from eight starts. Missed the frame latest (25.63) when fourth over 450m at Grafton in a Grade 4/5. Rates on top and should go close. SYDNEY KEEPING (7) has a strong overall record having five wins and three places from 11 starts including a last start success (22.57) over 401m at Richmond. Tends to go well on this box draw. Will go close here with a clear run. RISE UP NISMO (2) stalked the lead after a clean break from the tricky draw and went on to finish third (24.99) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 450m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to be in this for a long way. SIGN ACTION (4) was in the money last time at The Gardens (29.96) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 5.5 lengths second. Loves this draw, having won three of five starts.",
